<h1><i class="fa fa-search"></i>Searching News</h1>

<ol class="breadcrumb">
	<li><a href="#help"><i class="fa fa-question-circle"></i>Help</a></li>
	<li><a href="#help/sharing-news"><i class="fa fa-newspaper"></i>Sharing News</a></li>
	<li><i class="fa fa-search"></i>Searching News</li>
</ol>

<div class="content">
	<p>Sometimes it's handy to be able to search your posts to find just the right one.  <%= application.name %> allows a variety of searching options. </p> 

	<ol>
		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-search"></i>The Search Menu</h2>
			<p>Searching news posts is done by mousing over the "Search" menu on the header bar. When you select a search menu item, a search box of the selected type will appear in the header bar. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="dropdown menu" src="images/help/sharing-news/searching-news/search-menu@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search Menu</div>
			</div>		
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-quote-left"></i>Search by Message</h2>
			<p>The most commonly used search is to be able to search your posts by the message content. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/sharing-news/searching-news/search-by-message@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search By Message</div>
			</div>	
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-calendar-alt"></i>Search by Date</h2>
			<p>We can also search by date to find messages posted before or after a certain date, on a particular date. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/sharing-news/searching-news/search-by-date-before@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search By Date Before</div>
			</div>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/sharing-news/searching-news/search-by-date-equals@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search By Date Equals</div>
			</div>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/sharing-news/searching-news/search-by-date-after@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search By Date After</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-thumbs-up"></i>Search by Num Likes</h2>
			<p>We can also search by the number of likes in order to find comments by popularity. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/sharing-news/searching-news/search-by-num-likes-greater-than@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search By Likes Greater Than</div>
			</div>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/sharing-news/searching-news/search-by-num-likes-equal-to@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search By Likes Equal To</div>
			</div>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/sharing-news/searching-news/search-by-num-likes-less-than@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search By Likes Less Than</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-comment"></i>Search by Num Comments</h2>
			<p>We can also search by the number of comments in order to find comments that have been heavily discussed. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/sharing-news/searching-news/search-by-num-comments-greater-than@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search By Comments Greater Than</div>
			</div>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/sharing-news/searching-news/search-by-num-comments-equal-to@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search By Comments Equal To</div>
			</div>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/sharing-news/searching-news/search-by-num-comments-less-than@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search By Comments Less Than</div>
			</div>
		</li>
	</ol>
</div>